Job Description
Errands Services, an emerging telemarketing company is looking for motivated individuals who have the passion to learn and grow professionally as well as personally. The company offers, apart from great pay packages, a chance at cultural exposure, develop communication skills and confidence that will enable its members to possess unparalleled professional traits. Errands Services aims at providing equal growth opportunities for all employees. To be a part of our company, you should: -be highly proficient in English -have impeccable conversational and communication skills -have a can-do attitude -be willing to learn and grow -be motivated -be available 10:00PM to 07:00AM Pakistan Standard time, Monday to Friday
Job Specification
The role offered by the company entails: -out-bound calling -direct selling -appointment setting -information collection -'close' complete sales In remunerative terms, the company offers: -PKR 15,000 basic salary -commissions 1,000PKR to -bonuses -special performance-based incentives and give-aways (iPhones, motorbikes, cellular phones, cash prizes, complementary dinners and so on)
